org.apache.drill.exec.physical.impl.xsort.managed

Class TestCopier

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest
      • org.apache.drill.test.DrillTest
        • org.apache.drill.test.SubOperatorTest
          • org.apache.drill.exec.physical.impl.xsort.managed.TestCopier

  • public class TestCopier
extends SubOperatorTest
    Light-weight sanity test of the copier class. The implementation has been used in production, so the tests here just check for the obvious cases.

    Note, however, that if significant changes are made to the copier, then additional tests should be added to re-validate the code.
